<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2020-01-27</DATELINE><TITLE>Potential for global spread of a novel coronavirus from China</TITLE><BODY>An epidemic of a novel coronavirus emerged from Wuhan, China, in late December 2019 and has since spread to several large Chinese cities. Should a scenario arise where this coronavirus spreads more broadly across China, we evaluate how patterns of international disease transmission could change.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>